ction remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"screening_date\\\" label: \\\"Screening date\\\" purpose: \\\"Record when eligibility screening was performed.\\\" data_type: \\\"date\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Recruitment and screening, page 3\\\" confidence: \\\"medium\\\" notes: - \\\"A screening date is implied but not explicitly named as a CRF field.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"inferred_supporting_field\\\" rationale: \\\"A dated screening assessment is necessary to evaluate look-back periods stated by the protocol.\\\" confidence_percent: 90 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"inc01_informed_consent\\\" label: \\\"Informed consent inclusion criterion met\\\" purpose: \\\"Confirm that informed consent has been obtained.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 1, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" - locator: \\\"Ethical issues and dissemination, page 7\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: [] inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"age_years\\\" label: \\\"Age\\\" purpose: \\\"Record age in years as evidence for the age eligibility criterion.\\\" data_type: \\\"number\\\" required: null unit: \\\"years\\\" range: minimum: null maximum: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 2, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The inclusion interval is 30 through 65 years.\\\" - \\\"The form must retain out-of-range values to document screen failures.\\\" - \\\"Integer versus fractional-year precision is not stated.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"height_cm\\\" label: \\\"Height\\\" purpose: \\\"Record height in centimetres for the BMI calculation.\\\" data_type: \\\"number\\\" required: true unit: \\\"cm\\\" range: minimum: null maximum: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Anthropometric measurements, page 5\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The user specified centimetres as the capture unit for this BMI calculation.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review is required for the height result.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"weight_kg\\\" label: \\\"Weight\\\" purpose: \\\"Record weight in kilograms for the BMI calculation.\\\" data_type: \\\"number\\\" required: true unit: \\\"kg\\\" range: minimum: null maximum: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Anthropometric measurements, page 5\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The user specified kilograms as the capture unit for this BMI calculation.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review is required for the weight result.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"bmi\\\" label: \\\"Body mass index (BMI)\\\" purpose: \\\"Calculate body mass index from weight in kilograms and height in metres squared.\\\" data_type: \\\"number\\\" required: false unit: \\\"kg/m²\\\" range: minimum: null maximum: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: type: \\\"bmi\\\" height_concept_id: \\\"height_cm\\\" weight_concept_id: \\\"weight_kg\\\" decimal_places: 2 source_refs: - locator: \\\"Anthropometric measurements, page 5\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The protocol defines BMI as weight (kg) divided by height squared (m²).\\\" - \\\"The user specified rounding the displayed result to two decimal places.\\\" - \\\"The user requested these anthropometric fields in the current Screening/Eligibility form; the protocol describes them as study anthropometric measurements rather than an eligibility criterion.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review is required for the derived BMI result.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"inc02_age_30_to_65\\\" label: \\\"Age 30-65 years inclusion criterion met\\\" purpose: \\\"Record whether the protocol age criterion is satisfied.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 2, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"Consistency check candidate: true only when age is within the inclusive interval 30-65 years.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"newly_diagnosed_osa\\\" label: \\\"Newly diagnosed obstructive sleep apnoea\\\" purpose: \\\"Record newly diagnosed OSA status for the diagnostic inclusion criterion.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 3, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: [] inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"full_night_lab_psg_completed\\\" label: \\\"Full-night in-laboratory polysomnography completed\\\" purpose: \\\"Record the diagnostic method used to establish OSA eligibility.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 3, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: [] inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"screening_ahi\\\" label: \\\"Screening apnoea-hypopnoea index\\\" purpose: \\\"Record the PSG AHI used to assess diagnostic eligibility.\\\" data_type: \\\"number\\\" required: null unit: \\\"events/hour\\\" range: minimum: null maximum: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Diagnostic criteria and Inclusion criteria item 3, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" - locator: \\\"Recruitment and screening, page 3\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The qualifying threshold is at least 15 events/hour.\\\" - \\\"The field must retain values below 15 to document screen failures.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"inc03_osa_diagnostic_criterion\\\" label: \\\"Newly diagnosed OSA with qualifying PSG AHI inclusion criterion met\\\" purpose: \\\"Record whether the combined diagnostic inclusion criterion is satisfied.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 3, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"Consistency check candidate: newly diagnosed OSA, qualifying full-night in-laboratory PSG, and AHI at least 15 events/hour.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"cpap_one_night_use_hours\\\" label: \\\"CPAP use during one-night tolerance assessment\\\" purpose: \\\"Record CPAP use duration supporting the tolerance inclusion criterion.\\\" data_type: \\\"number\\\" required: null unit: \\\"hours\\\" range: minimum: null maximum: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 4, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The qualifying threshold is at least 4 hours during one night.\\\" - \\\"The field must retain values below 4 hours to document screen failures.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"inc04_cpap_tolerance\\\" label: \\\"CPAP tolerance inclusion criterion met\\\" purpose: \\\"Record whether the participant tolerated at least 4 hours of CPAP during one night.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 4, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"Consistency check candidate: true only when one-night CPAP use is at least 4 hours.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"inc05_no_other_trial_last_3_months\\\" label: \\\"No participation in another clinical trial during the past 3 months\\\" purpose: \\\"Record whether the recent clinical-trial participation inclusion criterion is satisfied.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 5, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: [] inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"inc06_able_complete_tests_followup\\\" label: \\\"Able to complete relevant tests and follow-up\\\" purpose: \\\"Record whether the participant can complete protocol assessments and follow-up.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria item 6, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: [] inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"exc01_severe_systemic_disease\\\" label: \\\"Severe systemic disease exclusion criterion present\\\" purpose: \\\"Record severe systemic disease, including the protocol examples of cardiac, hepatic, or renal failure.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Exclusion criteria item 1, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The examples are not treated as an exhaustive controlled list.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"exc02_psychiatric_condition\\\" label: \\\"Psychiatric condition exclusion criterion present\\\" purpose: \\\"Record a disqualifying psychiatric condition, including the protocol examples.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Exclusion criteria item 2, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"Depression, mania, and schizophrenia are examples, not an exhaustive controlled list.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"exc03_neurological_disease\\\" label: \\\"Neurological disease exclusion criterion present\\\" purpose: \\\"Record a disqualifying neurological disease, including the protocol examples.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Exclusion criteria item 3, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"Head trauma, brain tumour, epilepsy, stroke, transient ischaemic attack, and coma are examples, not an exhaustive controlled list.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"exc04_other_sleep_disorder\\\" label: \\\"Sleep disorder other than OSA exclusion criterion present\\\" purpose: \\\"Record a disqualifying non-OSA sleep disorder or specified central-apnoea/hypoventilation condition.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Exclusion criteria item 4, page 2\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"The protocol names narcolepsy, insomnia, chronic sleep deprivation, REM behaviour disorder, restless legs syndrome, central sleep apnoea with at least 50% of AHI from central apnoeas, and obesity hypoventilation syndrome.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"exc05_substance_or_restricted_medication\\\" label: \\\"Alcoholism, drug addiction, or restricted medication exclusion criterion present\\\" purpose: \\\"Record whether the compound substance-use and medication exclusion criterion is present.\\\" data_type: \\\"boolean\\\" required: null unit: null range: null options: [] visible_when: null required_when: null calculation: null source_refs: - locator: \\\"Exclusion criteria item 5, pages 2-3\\\" confidence: \\\"high\\\" notes: - \\\"Alcohol thresholds are sex-specific and expressed as standard drinks per week or per day.\\\" - \\\"The criterion also includes drug addiction, psychotropic-drug use, current sedative use, or narcotic use.\\\" - \\\"Whether to split this compound criterion into separate evidence fields requires Gate A approval.\\\" inference: kind: \\\"protocol_explicit\\\" rationale: null confidence_percent: 100 coding: status: \\\"unresolved\\\" rationale: \\\"Official CDASHIG v2.1 mapping review completed; specialist candidate selection remains pending.\\\" - concept_id: \\\"exc06_prior_osa_therapy\